}

### KB apply — follow-up
POST {{ONBOARD_API_BASE_URL}}/onboard/projects/{{PROJECT_ID}}/sync/kb/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{OPERATOR_JWT}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "syncRunId": "{{SYNC_RUN_ID}}",
  "confirmApply": true,
  "idempotencyKey": "pilot-apply-005",
  "applyScope": "FOLLOW_UP_SETTINGS_ONLY"
}

### Get sync runs
GET {{ONBOARD_API_BASE_URL}}/onboard/projects/{{PROJECT_ID}}/sync-runs
Authorization: Bearer {{OPERATOR_JWT}}

### Get KB plan preview
GET {{ONBOARD_API_BASE_URL}}/onboard/projects/{{PROJECT_ID}}/sync/kb/plan-preview
Authorization: Bearer {{OPERATOR_JWT}}

